sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as jwt-test-client Pod
    participant CSI as SPIFFE CSI Driver
    participant Agent as SPIRE Agent
    participant Server as SPIRE Server
    participant OIDC as SPIRE OIDC Discovery
    participant KC as Keycloak

    Note over Client,KC: JWT-SVID Authentication Flow

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note right of Client: Step 1: JWT-SVID Fetch
        Client->>CSI: Mount /spiffe-workload-api/spire-agent.sock
        CSI-->>Client: Socket available
        Client->>Agent: Fetch JWT-SVID<br/>(audience: Keycloak realm)
        Agent->>Server: Request JWT-SVID<br/>(SPIFFE ID: spiffe://example.org/ns/rhbk-demo/sa/myclient)
        Server->>Server: Sign JWT with private key
        Server-->>Agent: JWT-SVID
        Agent-->>Client: JWT-SVID<br/>(sub: spiffe://example.org/ns/rhbk-demo/sa/myclient)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note right of Client: Step 2: Token Request
        Client->>KC: POST /realms/spiffe/protocol/openid-connect/token<br/>grant_type=client_credentials<br/>client_assertion_type=urn:ietf:params:oauth:client-assertion-type:jwt-spiffe<br/>client_assertion=<JWT-SVID>
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note right of KC: Step 3: JWT-SVID Validation
        KC->>KC: Extract sub from JWT-SVID<br/>(spiffe://example.org/ns/rhbk-demo/sa/myclient)
        KC->>KC: Find Client by jwt.credential.sub
        KC->>KC: Get SPIFFE IdP by jwt.credential.issuer (alias: spiffe)
        KC->>OIDC: GET /.well-known/openid-configuration
        OIDC-->>KC: JWKS URI
        KC->>OIDC: GET /keys (JWKS)
        OIDC->>Server: Fetch Bundle (Public Keys)
        Server-->>OIDC: Bundle
        OIDC-->>KC: JWKS
        KC->>KC: Verify JWT-SVID signature<br/>with JWKS public key
        KC->>KC: Validate JWT claims<br/>(sub, iss, aud, exp)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note right of KC: Step 4: Access Token Issuance
        KC->>KC: Authentication successful
        KC->>KC: Generate Access Token<br/>(client_id=myclient)
        KC-->>Client: HTTP 200 OK<br/>{<br/>  "access_token": "eyJhbGci...",<br/>  "expires_in": 300,<br/>  "token_type": "Bearer"<br/>}
    end

    Note over Client,KC: ✅ Authentication Complete
